d magnetic field is in tens times stronger and is\nnot contaminated by the magnetic background of a bulky diamond anvil cell. This\ntechnique can be a powerful tool for the screening of new superconducting\nmaterials, the study of multiphase, contaminated samples, or samples with a low\nsuperconducting fraction at ambient pressure too.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2022 16:08:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 25 Sep 2022 18:31:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
