val inside\nthe 2016 solar gap, thus constraining the missed eruption to 2016.78 +- 0.10.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2022 18:32:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
