nergy. Finally, we note that the energy and velocity of the\ndelayed outflow in AT2018hyz are intermediate between those of past\nnon-relativistic TDEs (e.g., ASASSN-14li, AT2019dsg) and the relativistic TDE\nSw\\,J1644+57. We suggest that such delayed outflows may be common in TDEs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2022 21:34:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-26"}
