hmarking set of solutes and chemical\nreactions in water. The method is additionally validated by performing\nprospective (QM)ML/MM MD simulations of retinoic acid in water and\nS-adenoslymethioniat interacting with cytosine in water. The results indicate\nthat the $\\Delta$-learning GCNN model is a valuable alternative for (QM)ML/MM\nMD simulations of condensed-phase systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 06:37:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2022 10:59:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-05"}
