linear\nvalley Hall systems can support rich variety of new self-sustained topological\nstates and may inspire their investigation in other nonlinear systems, such as\natomic vapours and polariton condensates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 08:23:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-30"}
