{"id":"2207.02115","submitter":"Amit Maji","authors":"Satyabrata Majee and Amit Maji","title":"Wold-type decomposition for $\\mathcal{U}_n$-twisted contractions","comments":"20 pages, title changed and revised. To appear in Journal of\n  Mathematical Analysis and Applications","journal-ref":null,"doi":null,"report-no":null,"categories":"math.FA","license":"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","abstract":"  Let $n>1$, and $\\{U_{ij}\\}$ for $1 \\leq i < j \\leq n$ be $\\binom{n}{2}$\ncommuting unitaries on a Hilbert space $\\mathcal{H}$ such that\n$U_{ji}:=U^*_{ij}$. An $n$-tuple of contractions $(T_1, \\dots, T_n)$ on\n$\\mathcal{H}$ is called $\\mathcal{U}_n$-twisted contraction with respect to a\ntwist $\\{U_{ij}\\}_{i<j}$ if $T_1, \\dots, T_n$ satisfy \\[ T_iT_j=U_{ij}T_jT_i;\n\\hspace{0.5cm} \\hspace{1cm} T_i^*T_j= U^*_{ij}T_jT_i^* \\hspace{0.5cm}\n\\mbox{and} \\hspace{0.5cm} T_kU_{ij} =U_{ij}T_k \\] for all $i,j,k=1, \\dots, n$\nand $i \\neq j$.\n  We obtain a recipe to calculate the orthogonal spaces of the Wold-type\ndecomposition for $\\mathcal{U}_n$-twisted contractions on Hilbert spaces. As a\nby-product, a new proof as well as complete structure for\n$\\mathcal{U}_2$-twisted (or pair of doubly twisted) and $\\mathcal{U}_n$-twisted\nisometries have been established.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2022 19:00:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 22 Oct 2022 12:53:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 19:20:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-21"}
